<br>
Go to South Qeynos to the little pond by Fireprides (plate armor shop).  If you can get a bind right here, all the better, if not, it isn't that big of a deal as long as you are bound someplace close.  You will see a NPC named Lamar there.  Go into the aqueducts  (the ent is in the pool right beside the plate shop) and when you come out you will see three red spots on the floor.  Qubert (lvl 3 to 5) spawns here.  Kill him and sometimes you will loot a tattered dress.  Give it to Lamar and you will either get hematite or a golden ear stud (+3 int).  You can get xp until lvl 10 at the spawn point, and the ear stud sells for 30pp each or 50pp a set on nameless.  (for this use the Earth pet because Qubert will jump in the water to kill himself and steal your loot if he isn't rooted)<br>
<br>
As far as pets go, I use water a lot.  It seems that I am always hunting something with a poison, and the water pet is nice for this.<br>
<br>
Enjoy<br>
